1)filter function = opiadipote sinartisi exi orismata vars kai epistrefi true/false
  thelo oi times ton vars na tis tiroun

  kathe var mpori na exi poles teties sinartisis

  px ?i     (> ?i 20) (< ?i 40)
     ?i,?j  (= (+ ?i ?j) 10)


2)Pote tis efarmozo

  1 argument otan diabazo mia sxesi
  2 arguments ean anikoun stin idia sxesi otan diabazo tin sxesi

  >= 2 arguments sto idio tree otan kano ta join
   *kathe function exi os key tin teleutea var pou xriazome gia na tin efarmososo (simfona me to sorted vars)

  >=2 arguments se xexoristo tree/single
   *kathe function exi os key to index tou teleuteou dentrou/single pou xriazete kai tin teleutea metabliti
    pou xriazete apo auto,otan tin diabazo tin efarmozo

    Bazo se mia seira ta singles kai dentra
    px index 8 ean exo 3 singles simeni 5o dentro

  Kathos bazo times ean blepo oti den tirite i sinthiki petao oli tin grami



3)Pos tis efarmozo

  px
  (= (+ ?i (- ?j 2) 10))

  Mporo na to do san string pou
   stis thesis 4 eos 7 einai i ?i
   stin thesis 10 eos 15 eiani i ?j

  Kano antikatastasi metabliti me tin timi,kai eval

  (eval (read-string "(+ 2 (- 1 2) 10)"))

4)problima
  ean oi metablites anikoun se diaforetika dentra,i se single

  thelo na xero se pia dentra anikoun
  mporoun na ektimithoun otan oti xriazonte apo kathe dentro exi ektimithi
  etsi prepei na to kano,gia na petao oti einai na petaxo prin to paraxo

  1)xorizo tis functions se autes pou anikoun se 1 dentro i single

  2)autes pou anikoun se ena tis efarmozo kanonika sto dentro/single

  3)meta brisko pia dentra xriazonte autes pou menoun kai tis efarmozo se auta
    aferontas grames apo auta
    *i to kano auto otan bazo to teleuteo dentro,stin teleutea metabliti pou xriazete


  Eidi filter functions

  1)1 var (single i se tree)
  2)2 vars same relation
  3)n>=2 vars same tree
  4)n>=2 vars diferrent trees

  Arika tha kano ta filter gia ta 1),2),3)

  1)1 var ginonte panta kata tin anagnosi tis sxesis (done)
  2)2 vars same relation panta kata tin anagnosi tis sxesis (done)
  3)n>=2 vars same tree,otan kano ta joins
    tin stigmi pou tha balo tin teleutea var pou xriazome sto tree

4)filter emine to na efarmoso filter sto cartesian product
